README for Example "fatfs-sd"
-----------------------------

PICtail Daughter Board for SD and MMC Cards may be installed in SPI1 or SPI2 ports on Explorer16.

Make following for select SPI port:
1) to select SPI1
    - install PICtail Dauther Board to SPI1 connector (see Explorer16 documentation);
    - in file "main.h" set define SD_SPI1 (SPI1 port).
2) to select SPI2
    - install PICtail Dauther Board to SPI2 connector (see Explorer16 documentation);
    - in file "main.h" set define SD_SPI2 (SPI2 port).
